{"tid":2320058,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周大福屈臣氏及OK便利店等有份領取新一期工資補貼","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1219a1598838d66e7d2342b4c8af63beeab45bd3","tid":2320058,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:25:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564621-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564621-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqdEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=c6113370\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564621-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9ab43e72\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564621-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃秘書處公布新一批領取第二期工資補貼的僱主名單，涉及近4500名僱主，發放工資補貼額約10億元，涵蓋今年9月至11月，承諾受薪僱員人數超過48000人。<br />\n<br />\n新一批僱主名單中，周大福珠寶金行有限公司獲發補貼7700多萬元，涉及2835名員工。OK便利店有限公司獲6100多萬補貼，涉及3540員工。<br />\n<br />\n另外，屈臣氏零售（香港）有限公司的工資補貼額約7100多萬元，承諾受薪僱員2960人。"},{"pid":"7d82c96da786e302fbd6cda2b3ab2341b4af7c54","tid":2320058,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}